{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider/colorActiveIndicatorCustomSelectedPressed":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider\/colorActiveIndicatorCustomSelectedPressed","title":"colorActiveIndicatorCustomSelectedPressed","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Has for value token colors.actionPressed"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"colorActiveIndicatorCustomSelectedPressed","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MultipleColorSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"c:@M@OUDSTokensSemantic@objc(cs)MultipleColorSemanticToken","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider\/coloractiveindicatorcustomselectedpressed"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebarcomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBarComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BarComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Bar"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of colors ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllColorSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and effects (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllEffectSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBarComponentTokensProvider"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png"}]}}}